c: 12
v: 65
t: "When they opened their baggage, they discovered that their money had been returned to them. \"Father!\" They cried with joy, \"What more can we ask for? Here is our money returned back to us. We will buy more food for our family, we will take good care of our brother and obtain an extra camel load of grain. This way, it will be easy to add another camel load of grain"